48
00:02:08,720 --> 00:02:11,740
for those stories or things in those stories,

49
00:02:11,740 --> 00:02:13,640
and that skewed their results.

50
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:15,880
Once they identified those factors,

51
00:02:15,880 --> 00:02:17,570
they were able to take them into account

52
00:02:17,570 --> 00:02:20,280
and the model was very accurate after that.

